# Desktop build configuration. Copy to `desktop/.env` (gitignored) and set your
# real backend endpoint. This value is injected at build time into the frontend
# (VITE_API_BASE) and the CSP connect-src — it is the ONLY place the backend
# hostname lives, so committed source carries no infrastructure details.
#
# Your Tailscale backend (tailnet-only HTTPS), e.g.:
CC_DESKTOP_API_BASE=https://host.your-tailnet.ts.net:8443
